{"view":"article","slug":"2x2-beginner-1-look","category":"2x2","subcategory":null,"topDir":"2x2","title":{"en":"2x2 Beginner 1-Look二阶入门全预判"},"content":{"en":"<p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">2x2 Beginner 1-Look二阶入门全预判</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image3.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image5.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p>Assume yellow FF. Predict OLL: track any 3 white stickers; Then predict EG: track any 3 non-white stickers on any 3 white pieces. For cases where all yellow pieces are in first layer, do pre-AUF to make better EG. Alg of left case <strong>R U R' U R2</strong> moves purple, green, orange pieces in right image by <strong>y2 z, y2 z +</strong>, <strong>y2 z F</strong>. Notation: fixed piece, piece by pure rotating, twist piece, piece by 1 or 2 moves, piece by 2 moves. + = CW, - = CCW.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R2 y2 z (+, F)\"><strong>R U R' U R2 y2 z (+, F)</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p>1<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image9.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p>2<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image11.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image13.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p>3<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image15.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/2x2-beginner-1-look/en/image17.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><